	(text "TODO:\n\nX MOVE SYMBOLS TO OH LIBRARIES\nX POINT AFFECTED SYMBOLS/FOOTPRINTS/STEP AT OH LIBRARIES\n\nPCB:\nMINIMIZE RS485 STUB LENGTH BY TUNING A/B TRACES\nADD 2 VIAs EACH TO VCC AND GND ON THE TRANSCEIVER\nX CHECK SILKSCREEN, ADJUST AS REQUIRED\nX ADD RS485 SHIELD DRAIN SCREW TERMINAL\nGENERATE STEP FILE\nGENERATE SCHEMATIC PDF\nGENERATE JLCPCB PACKAGE\nCOPY MFG AND PDF TO RELEASE FOLDER"
