	(text "1) J5 / IO CONNECTORS MAY NOT FUNCTION WITH DCS-BIOS WHILE MASTER FUNCTIONALITY IS IN USE.\n\n2) ABSIS RS485 BUS SPECIFICATION\n   2.1) BUS IS HALF DUPLEX: EITHER TRANSMITTING OR RECIEVING AT ANY GIVEN TIME.\n   2.2) PIN FUNCTION: R: DATA OUTPUT / D: DATA INPUT / DE HAS INTERNAL PULL-DOWN \n        (DRIVER DISABLED BY DEFAULT) / RE HAS INTERNAL PULL-UP (RECIEVER DISABLED BY DEFAULT)\n   2.3) CIRCUIT CONTAINS OPEN, SHORT, AND IDLE BUS FAILSAFE WHICH PREVENTS THE SYSTEM FROM \n        INTERPRETING ELECTRICAL NOISE AS VALID DATA.\n   2.4) THVD1410DR TRANSCIEVER OPERATES WITH TTL LEVEL INPUTS. (LOGIC HIGH: 2V - VCC / \n        LOGIC LOW: 0V - .8VCC)\n   2.5) CAUTION: AS CABLE LENGTH INCREASES, DATA RATE DECREASES PROPORTIONALLY."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 14.478 41.91 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "8e6d1436-3b15-45fd-a7fc-588e647e3bfe")
	)
